data.description: Spacious 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, 2-story home built on a great sized lot in the highly sought after City of Cibolo. The main living room boasts plenty of space and ample natural light. Great open floor plan with a flex room/office immediately upon entering. The large kitchen has lots of cabinet and countertop space. Roof recently replaced in 2022. Enjoy entertaining in the cozy loft upstairs. The large backyard and extra space allow you to enjoy the outdoors and is perfect for relaxing or having group gatherings. This home is conveniently located close to shopping and restaurants and the location allows easy access to IH-35, IH-10 and FM 78. The Schertz-Cibolo-Universal City Independent School District, with schools only minutes from the home. The neighborhood pool and playground are also walking distance! VA assumable loan 3.75!
